# HotDocs: Embedded

Follow these steps to embed HotDocs in an already existing Rails application:

```bash
bundle add hotdocs
bin/rails hotdocs:install
```

You can now start the server and visit HotDocs:

```bash
bin/rails server
open http://127.0.0.1:3000/hotdocs
```
